    "stem": "A customer is long three soybean futures contracts at 425 1/4 cents per bushel. Initial margin is $0.12 per bushel, and maintenance margin is $0.10 per bushel. The contract's minimum tick is 1/4 cent. At what trade price will the customer receive a margin call?",
